Name: project_assignment
Description: Indicates if a project is selected for sprint planning

Name: team_assignment
Description: Assignment of a team to a project

Name: worker_assignment
Description: Assignment of a worker to a task

Name: skill_level
Description: Proficiency level of a worker in a skill

Name: task_effort_assigned
Description: Effort allocated to a task by a worker

Name: user_story_priority
Description: Priority level of a user story

Name: story_points_assigned
Description: Story points assigned to a user story

Name: velocity_sprints_count
Description: Number of sprints used to calculate velocity

Name: roadmap_objective_weight
Description: Weight assigned to a roadmap objective

Name: documentation_update_count
Description: Number of times documentation was updated

Name: retrospective_improvement_actions
Description: Number of improvement actions from retrospective

Name: scrum_board_column_count
Description: Number of columns on a Scrum board
